Q: If you have only recently finished your programme/finished your final exams,?
A: parchments will not be ordered from QQI until your official results are released. They will then take up to 8 weeks to arrive with us at DBS. Parchments are first distributed at the graduation ceremonies but exceptions can be made on a case by case basis for early release.
